data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers approximately 1651 sqft of space! There is carpet throughout with ceramic tile flooring in the kitchen and bathrooms. The living area and kitchen feature a vaulted ceiling, providing an open feel. The kitchen comes complete with black electric appliances, granite countertops, a pantry, and a dining area. In the dining area there is a door that leads to the backyard features a large covered patio and a wooden privacy fence.
